{"tid":1604541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]香港出現討伐隊","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:02:35.000Z","uid":28970,"like":280,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f63e062861acc22b4970c685f5dc666b0c2b95","tid":1604541,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"早幾日發左個夢 <br />\n夢入面有朋友同我講佢果區好多休班狗畜 咁都未算是嚴重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地發現依種生物有啲打完會跌啲棍(裝備)出黎 <br />\n佢話佢地討伐過程一定要打到重傷<br />\n事後更加冇任何人會上報同埋公報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢相信一定有更加多人做 <br />\n如果佢話會覆桌咁一定要打撚到佢話唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然佢會厄你 依個時候就到佢家爺仔乸出動<br />\n佢話記得對家點打我地我地10倍奉還 <br />\n畜方依加咁難得先穩定到軍心 一定唔會公開喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論 大家一定要小心行事<br />\n手套所有保護自己一定要做好<br />\n依加係有人做 但太少人效率太低<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將被動轉為主動 暗地裡主動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講到咁都差啲以前係真 之後就夢醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM1rEyD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM1rEyD.jpg&h=313ee5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXpT30j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXpT30j.jpg&h=11e9790b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOSeOr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOSeOr3.png&h=e83c0b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FH2Xkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FH2Xkq.jpg&h=500801af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bELDvFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbELDvFq.png&h=80ef5bba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c76b9bcfea60a631a908938d75141135e15e9b7","tid":1604541,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef1d48f283c3ff1cf6afe552b1168c4d0216ec4","tid":1604541,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284641f348e43ef50d087e2218aa7794d0c00454","tid":1604541,"uid":272976,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"拿好老實講，要做嘅唔會講出嚟"},{"pid":"51205337bc55a91e41a39d674467a1c1e2944a50","tid":1604541,"uid":38991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"真？"},{"pid":"fbf746cf5e233aa5e4777896e3f5acf149db9668","tid":1604541,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87a8cc22f64e58bb82b1e196ed128128a595ab96","tid":1604541,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠膽覆卓咪祝佢家宅平安囉<br />\nd死黑警話呢句落唔到案唔受理ga<br />\n我俾人耍走過啦屌佢老母"},{"pid":"cd18aa573c0c9ebfd3236e3dff0ac3818de5c6a0","tid":1604541,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"［十一］暴風雨前夕 文宣組做野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604081</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b25fe6d76ee21ca9f944abc572e65993c9d6ab9b","tid":1604541,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rULjZBu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrULjZBu.jpg&h=77ead16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9NuCn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9NuCn9.jpg&h=a6313231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"